The monic polynomial $P_N(x; \varphi)$ has roots $r_k(\varphi)$ and can be written as
\begin{equation}
P_N(x; \varphi) = \prod_{k=0}^{N-1}(x - r_k(\varphi)) = \sum_{k=0}^N (-1)^k e_k \, x^{N-k},
\end{equation}
